rune
Runes?  I'm surprised you know about them.  Perhaps you would like to know 
more about the black rune.
black
The ability to open and close special portals rests with the power of 
certain runes.  Find Xerxes at the Chandre Library for information on the 
black rune.
portals
A secret portal has been well hidden in Darbonne Park itself.  It lies in 
a room infesteed with trolls.

